“Over 3 years ago, I started @vedaynclothingllc in NYC at the @nyhotelpenn 2019, right before Covid. The goal was to bring people together with fashion, art, and music, no matter what walks of life we come from. 

You should always be able to see things differently. So, with the help of @legalzoom, true story, I had a vision that was years into manifesting. 

Fast forward 3 years later, we had over 4 locations in #EastLondon and over 4 global publications. @iamdancrossley was the 1st U.K Artist for his Cargo Debut live then came Some features by @equate__ ft @onlyscorch, did some work with @byoung for @notion, and can’t forget y’all favorite #mobwives star ⭐️ @reneegraziano, who we did a custom piece for her. 

Also worked with @phynofino for @notion in the sown of a year. Then we had the biggest opportunity of all, being featured on @grmdaily for @cleanbandit Drive remix video, with over 2.4 million views, with @gracechatto and @wes.nelson rocking two custom-designed pieces handmade by myself & @vedaynclothingllc. 

This is for anyone out there, just know dreams turn into reality when you manifest it. Anything is possible, keep striving and setting the bar, there are no limits.

We have only just begun to new levels and heights.

V.E.D.A.Y.N.

We were asked if we could deliver three custom @vedaynclothingllc leather jackets for some of the biggest names in Europe and globally. 

The request was for designing these jackets for a major music production video, which was set to shoot within 72 hours. #Fyp 

I immediately got the team on a call and reached out to my tailor in London.

I must have been painting all night, but I didn’t mind it because seeing the finished product and vision come to life was amazing.

I just want to say, a year later, with  over 2.4 million views on @grmdaily , Just wanted to say big thank you to @cleanbandit @wes.nelson for trusting the vision and liking the jackets enough to wear them in the video, and thanks to my bro for making the link.
